{"comments":"Photo Filter — Simulates camera lens filters.\n\n## Industry Standard\n\nMirrors AE's Photo Filter effect which simulates optical lens filters:\n\n- **Warming Filters (81, 85)**: Add orange/amber tones\n- **Cooling Filters (80, 82)**: Add blue tones\n- **Color Filters**: Apply any color as a filter\n\n## Properties (All Animatable)\n\n| Property | Type | Min | Max | Behavior | Default |\n|----------|------|-----|-----|----------|---------|\n| filterType | FilterType | — | — | enum | Warming85 |\n| color.r | Number | 0.0 | 1.0 | clamps | varies |\n| color.g | Number | 0.0 | 1.0 | clamps | varies |\n| color.b | Number | 0.0 | 1.0 | clamps | varies |\n| density | Number | 0.0 | 100.0 | clamps | 25.0 |\n| preserveLuminosity | Boolean | — | — | — | true |\n\n## Mathematical Model\n\nPhoto filter applies color as an overlay blend at specified density:\n`result = lerp(original, blendedWithFilter, density / 100.0)`\n\nWhen preserveLuminosity is true, the luminance of the original is\nrestored after the color blend.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[111,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Motion/Effects/ColorCorrection/PhotoFilter.purs","start":[111,3]},"title":"Warming85"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[112,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Motion/Effects/ColorCorrection/PhotoFilter.purs","start":[112,3]},"title":"Warming81"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[113,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Motion/Effects/ColorCorrection/PhotoFilter.purs","start":[113,3]},"title":"WarmingLBA"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[114,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Motion/Effects/ColorCorrection/PhotoFilter.purs","start":[114,3]},"title":"Cooling80"},{"comments":nul